NAME:-		Laensword
FILENAME:-	/d/Emerald/telberin/wep/laensword.c
		/d/Emerald/telberin/wep/leansword_sh.c

MAXHIT:-	52
MAXPEN:-	50

SPECIAL:-	There are 5 classes of wielders:

	"Worthy"
		Not Undead, align => 900, average stat of 120+,
		WIS and DIS => 80

		"Worthy" wielders recieve the following benefits:
		52 hit, 50 pen, the sword glows when an undead or
		a very evil creature/person ( align <= -500) enters
		the environment of the wielder. (Note: this also
		reveals the wielder if they are hidden) The sword
		also protects the body as well as both arms (via
		query_protects()) and heals 18 hp/minute

	"good"
		Align >= 100 and one of the above stat or align
		requirements not met and not undead. These wielders
		get 52 hit, 50 pen, and no other bonuses.

	"neutral"
		Align -99 to 99 and not undead.
		20 hit, 15 pen

	"evil"
		align -899 to -100
		-100 hit/pen, impossible to hit with if align <= -900
		possible severe magic damage in combat (hit_me w/pen
		 of 500) and drop the weapon
		
		
PROPS:-		OBJ_M_NO_BUY, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC,
		MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO, OBJ_S_WIZINFO, OBJ_M_NO_STEAL

OBTAINABILITY:-	Very, very, very difficult. Must defeat Curan
		/d/Emerald/telberin/npc/curan.c


